kraken : tentacles of the deep , also known as deadly water , is a 2006 made-for-television natural horror b-movie produced by nu image films and brightlight pictures as a sci fi channel original film . it premiered on the sci fi channel on september 23 , 2006 . directed by tibor tak√°cs and starring charlie o'connell , victoria pratt , and jack scalia , the film focuses on a marine biologist and a sailor who join forces to find lost trojan treasures while battling the giant squid who killed the sailor 's parents while he was a child , and a treasure hunting mobster who wants the items for himself . the film was primarily panned by critics for the special effects , far-fetched plot , and scarcity of scenes involving the titular creature .